data.description: Lovingly cared for home conveniently located to Interstate 75, shopping and dining. The interior offers vaulted ceiling in the living room where the centerpiece of the room is a lovely, gas logs, fireplace. The living room is open to the dining area which leads to a spacious kitchen with a gas stove and ample cabinets. The guest bedrooms are larger than average and the bonus room could be another guest room. It would be a great guest room or teen suite, since it has its own 1/2 bath. The Owner's suite makes a king sized bed look small and the bathroom offers separate vanities, tub and shower. The garage is oversized and the driveway is perfect for all your extra vehicles and those of your guests. The backyard is the place to relax out of the sun in the screened in porch or for a little sunshine you can enjoy the open air deck. The house sits back off the road and offers much privacy. This is the house you've been looking for. Come make it your home!
